    - IMS: corrupt SIP 200 OK → P-CSCF retransmits per RFC 3261 §17
    - 5G: drop NRF discovery response → AMF retries with backoff
    Log the chaos event and recovery path at all three log levels
    INTERVIEW narration: "This is how real networks handle node failures"

